text: The Free Lance–Star is a newspaper based in Fredericksburg, Virginia. The newspaper is published daily and serves many counties surrounding Fredericksburg. The Free Lance was first published on January 27, 1885. In 1900, the Free Lance operation merged with its competitor, The Fredericksburg Daily Star. The two merged newspapers changed the name to The Free Lance–Star. == Other websites == * Official site * Online version of print newspaper Category:Newspapers in the United States Category:Organizations based in Virginia
